An incomplete and yet highly enjoyable gallery of the wild wild world. The Spring/Summer 2020 Menswear presentations showcased at Milan – at Milano Moda Uomo, a selection of fashion shows for men held at the Milan Fair – followed by the Paris shows, which were showcased from 18 June until Sunday 23 June. From bold patterns and bright colours, oversized silhouettes and… Here is an incomplete yet striking gallery from the Paris Fashion Week Haute Couture shows.